OL,3,CGirl, 4, injured after empty vehicle
OL,4,C'rolls over her' in car park
OL,6,FPolice are appealing for witnesses
OL,7,Fafter an unattended vehicle "rolled
OL,8,Fover" a 4-year-old girl in a car park.
OL,10,FThe child was injured and has been
OL,11,Ftaken to hospital to be assessed.
OL,13,FIt happened in the car park near
OL,14,FMimosa Tea Garden, a popular cafe at
OL,15,FEastham Country Park on the banks of
OL,16,Fthe River Mersey in Wirral.
OL,18,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,19,Fscene on Green Lane at around 3.50pm
OL,20,Fon Saturday.
