OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1782038884
OL,3,CGirl, 4, injured after empty vehicle
OL,4,C'rolls over her' in car park
OL,6,FA statement from Merseyside Police
OL,7,Fsaid, "The owner of the vehicle
OL,8,Fremained at the scene and is helping
OL,9,Fpolice with their enquires."
OL,11,FOfficers have launched an
OL,12,Finvestigation and are appealing for
OL,13,Fanyone who saw the incident to contact
OL,14,Fthem via social media, on their
OL,15,Fwebsite or by calling 101.
OL,17,FAlternatively, witnesses can contact
OL,18,Fthe independent charity Crimestoppers
OL,19,Fanonymously online or by phoning 0800
OL,20,F555 111.
